{
  "texts": [
    "The pneumonia detection task aims to detect pneumonia from chest X-ray images.",
    "This task is based on the COVIDx dataset 30 that contains three classes, including normal people, non-COVID-19 infection, and COVID-19 viral infection.",
    "We consider four clients, e.g., hospitals, in the federated distillation framework.",
    "To simulate the non-IID data across clients, each of them only has one or two classes of chest X-ray images, and each class contains 1,000 images.",
    "Besides, we construct a proxy dataset for knowledge transfer, which contains all three classes, and each class has 500 unlabeled samples."
  ]
}